dialogue.text: <clip=player, cast>Eh... uhm... hello?!dsadasdasdas
<clip=player, cast>FgKeOKalLfOlf?sdddddddddddddddddddddddd
Yeah... I don't understand a thing...
*Fiona turns on their auto translator*
Hey there... I believe you can understand me now
I didn't know you were able to speak my language
Hehe... yeah, now I do
We from the village heard a loud weird noise and I volunteered to investigate
Are you perhaps responsible for this loud noise?
(Hmm, she must be talk about when I landed here)
Yeah... sorry about that. I've come here to search for a missing person
Have you perhaps seen some traveler that looks similar to me?
A traveler that looks like you... Not that I can recall
I can ask around the village for you but I doubt that anyone has seen someone as unique like you
That would be the buzz around town!
Anyways, I don't think I can allow passage for you to the village
I must discuss this with the elders first. You know how old people are, always wary of strangers
You're free to use the abandoned farmhouse behind you
You'll be able to farm, craft and sleep till your heart's content during your stay
Just be sure to plant the seeds inside of the garden and there'll be no problems
Oh, names, Jane by the way... forgot to mention that
Thanks Jane! My name is Fiona! Happy meeting you
Good luck with your search!
